# Trivy Ignore File
# This file suppresses specific vulnerabilities from Trivy scans
#
# Format: CVE-ID or GHSA-ID (one per line)
# Best Practice: Always document WHY and set review dates
#
# Example:
# CVE-2024-12345
# Reason: False positive - not exploitable in our context
# Expires: 2024-12-31
# Reviewed by: Security Team

# =============================================================================
# Currently no ignored vulnerabilities
# =============================================================================
# When adding entries:
# 1. Document the reason for ignoring
# 2. Set an expiration/review date
# 3. Get security team approval for HIGH/CRITICAL
# 4. Link to tracking ticket (Jira, GitHub issue)
